Brotli-X/
├── .github/workflows/ci.yml          # matrix: {ubuntu-22, macos-13, win-2022} × {clang, gcc, msvc}
├── cmake/                             # shared CMake helpers
├── scripts/                           # dev-env setup, docker, conda
├── vendor/                            # git-submodules or FetchContent
├── brotli-x/                          # entropy codec
├── kvshard/                           # lock-free KV
├── cachefly/                          # NVMe-oF read cache
├── qgan/                              # 4-bit GAN stack
├── topoopt/                           # AI planner
├── memspill/                          # CUDA ↔ CXL spiller
├── socketx/                           # user-space TCP over RDMA
├── flashinfer/                        # drop-in LLM kernels
└── nanolr/                            # 8-bit LR scheduler

Every sub-project has an identical interface:
  mkdir build && cd build
  cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release
  ctest --output-on-failure            # unit + micro-bench
  ./bench/bench_headline               # prints the claim